@host = http://localhost:5080

### 1) Run the two-agent workflow. Returns a drafted reply AWAITING human approval.
###    (Triage agent assesses the ticket -> Drafter agent writes the customer reply.)
POST {{host}}/workflow/triage
Content-Type: application/json

{ "message": "My order A1234 arrived with a cracked screen and I need a replacement before Friday." }

### 2) Inspect a draft by id (paste the id returned above).
GET {{host}}/workflow/DRF-xxxxxxxx

### 3) Approve a draft (the human-in-the-loop gate) before it would be sent.
POST {{host}}/workflow/DRF-xxxxxxxx/approve

### Empty message -> 400 Bad Request
POST {{host}}/workflow/triage
Content-Type: application/json

{ "message": "" }
